	dprr:hasNoteText "Monetalis. In MRR 2.434, and Index, 541, refer also to Crawford, RRC 1.278, no. 247, 133 B.C. See Syme, RP 1.278; perhaps a Calpurnius Lanarius, since the Pisones did not use the praenomen P.; Wiseman, NM 280, no. 528.[45]\n" .
